subject: This one speaks for itself...
author: Adriana Jones
full_text:
See endoffilewow.mp3 in my files folder.  This was the very end of the session my husband and I did at night in Charles Town, WV cemetery, on October 15.

Notice:
A man whose voice persists through several seconds of the file saying... "you...too...erchin...wonderful"  what the heck is erchin, lol!  Here you should also notice that between "erchin" and "wonderful" there is a definite station change "whine" sound...

Then you may also notice when I ask "Should we come back ever?"  A lady says, "Ever?" or "Never" can tell which....

We're  getting some pretty convincing stuff for having been doing less than a month.
